# jaetaan selittäviin ja vastemuuttujaan 
X = df.iloc[:,:8]
Y = df.iloc[:,8]
In [12]:
# luodaan malli ja sovitetaan muuttujat
reg = LogisticRegression()
reg.fit(X,Y)

print("Coefficients: ",reg.coef_)
print("Intercept: ", reg.intercept_)

In [20]:
# cross-validate
# number of folds
k = 10
scores = cross_val_score(estimator=reg,
                        X=X,
                        y=Y,
                        scoring="accuracy",
                        cv=k)
print("Accuracies from %d individual folds:" % k)
print(scores)
print("Accuracy calculated using %d-fold cross validation = %.3f" % (k, scores.mean()))
